import {useSelector} from 'react-redux'; import { CardBody, CardTitle, CardText, } from 'reactstrap'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import Error from '../components/Error'; import Loading from '../components/Loading'; const CurrentTournamentCardBody = ({ item}) => { const { id, name, date_utc, start_time, tournament_type, playoff_elimination_type, location, tournament_status, total_teams} = item; const isLoading = useSelector((state) => state.tournaments.isLoading); const errMsg = useSelector((state) => state.tournaments.errMsg); return ( <>
{name}
{tournament_status}
{date_utc} | {start_time}
{location}
{tournament_type}
{playoff_elimination_type}
Total Teams: {total_teams}
View Details
) } export default CurrentTournamentCardBody;
